        {
            "content_html": "<img src=\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/8225977?u=ebf8bbc30918fe9c36833005bebc027a65984f34&v=4\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" alt=\"\"/><br/>\n<h2 dir=\"auto\">Request for Mozilla Position on an Emerging Web Specification</h2>\n<ul dir=\"auto\">\n<li>Specification title: <code class=\"notranslate\">line-clamp</code> CSS property (collapse variant)</li>\n<li>Specification or proposal URL (if available): <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"1365126325\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/w3c/csswg-drafts/issues/7708\" data-hovercard-type=\"issue\" data-hovercard-url=\"/w3c/csswg-drafts/issues/7708/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/w3c/csswg-drafts/issues/7708\">w3c/csswg-drafts#7708</a></li>\n<li>Explainer URL (if available): <a href=\"https://github.com/Igalia/explainers/blob/main/css/line-clamp/README.md\">https://github.com/Igalia/explainers/blob/main/css/line-clamp/README.md</a></li>\n<li>Proposal author(s) (<code class=\"notranslate\">@</code>-mention GitHub accounts): <a class=\"user-mention notranslate\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/users/emilio/hovercard\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/emilio\">@emilio</a>, <a class=\"user-mention notranslate\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/users/bfgeek/hovercard\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/bfgeek\">@bfgeek</a>, <a class=\"user-mention notranslate\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/users/frivoal/hovercard\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/frivoal\">@frivoal</a></li>\n<li>Caniuse.com URL (optional):</li>\n<li>Bugzilla URL (optional):</li>\n<li>Mozillians who can provide input (optional): <a class=\"user-mention notranslate\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/users/emilio/hovercard\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/emilio\">@emilio</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">Other information</h3>\n<p dir=\"auto\">CSS Overflow Level 4 defines <code class=\"notranslate\">line-clamp</code> based on fragmentation (<a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-overflow-4/#line-clamp\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://drafts.csswg.org/css-overflow-4/#line-clamp</a>), but that is not feasible for Gecko to implement anytime soon. Due to that, <a class=\"user-mention notranslate\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/users/emilio/hovercard\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/emilio\">@emilio</a> opened <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"1365126325\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/w3c/csswg-drafts/issues/7708\" data-hovercard-type=\"issue\" data-hovercard-url=\"/w3c/csswg-drafts/issues/7708/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/w3c/csswg-drafts/issues/7708\">w3c/csswg-drafts#7708</a> to discuss a variant of <code class=\"notranslate\">line-clamp</code> that is based on hiding lines and boxes from paint instead (\"the collapse variant\"). There is no spec text written for this variant yet, but the CSSWG decided to greenlight both variants for prototyping, and in Chromium we are currently planning to prototype it, rather than the fragmentation-based variant.</p>",
